Package org.opendaylight.controller.sal.packet

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IDataPacketService
    Data Packet Services SAL provides to the components
    IListenDataPacket
    Interface that all the components that want to receive a dataPacket need to implement.
    IPluginInDataPacketService
    Data Packet Services exported by SouthBound plugins for SAL usage.
    IPluginOutDataPacketService
    Interface used by SAL to intercept any Data Packet coming from the southbound protocol plugins
  • Class Summary

    ARP
    Class that represents the ARP packet objects

    BitBufferHelper
    BitBufferHelper class that provides utility methods to - fetch specific bits from a serialized stream of bits - convert bits to primitive data type - like short, int, long - store bits in specified location in stream of bits - convert primitive data types to stream of bits
